title: Grateful Dead Live at Austin Municipal Auditorium on 1971-11-15
lineage: WAV > Samplitude Pro v10.2.1 > Izotope RX8 Advanced > Adobe Audition CC2022 > FLAC/16
description:
Set I
Truckin', Bertha, Playin' In The Band, Deal, Jack Straw, Loser, Beat It On Down The Line, Dark Star-> El Paso-> Dark Star-> Casey Jones, One More Saturday Night
Set II
Me & My Uncle, Ramble On Rose, Mexicali Blues, Brokedown Palace, Me And Bobby McGee, Cumberland Blues, Sugar Magnolia, You Win Again, Not Fade Away-> China Cat Sunflower Jam-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Not Fade Away, E: Johnny B. Goode

Comment
FM broadcast WREK - Other artist(s): NRPS
